\fBword_highlight\fP.
.TP 
\fBmono_markstar\fP
Character attribute of words emphasized like *this*. It depends on your
terminal which attributes are usable. See also \fBword_h_display_marks\fP and
\fBword_highlight\fP.
.TP 
\fBmono_markstroke\fP
Character attribute of words emphasized like \-this\-. It depends on your
