Keep posted articles in
\fI${TIN_HOMEDIR:\-"$HOME"}/Mail/\fP\fBposted_articles_file\fP.  If no filename is
set then postings will not be saved.  Default is 'posted'.
.TP 
\fBprint_header\fP
